node.text: #ad Here is me trying to game and get in charge of my personal finance at the same time, both things I really suck at. But thanks to Credit Karma, I no longer have to worry so much about my personal finance, which means I can suck at gaming in peace. @creditkarma is extremely useful at breaking down your scores and sharing little tips that can make a big difference in the long run. They help you track key parts of your finances all in one place and empowers you to APPLY with more confidence for credit cards and personal loans. For more tips on beating your personal finances head over to creditkarma.com and tune-in to a special collaboration between Credit Karma and The Cube @tbsnetwork’s new game-show airing Thursday nights at 9pm ET/PT!
